cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CL 

This paper deals with action recognition using visual features and semantic descriptors, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of word-vectors as a shared semantic space also suggests a possible connection to natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of videos as input data suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
